<h2>Proust - Flaubert - Ovid (Monographie)</h2>
<h3>Der Stoff, aus dem Erinnerungen sind</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='2035'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
